               <msContents>
                  <summary>Horologium for the Night Hours of Abba Giyorgis, ሰዓታት፡ ዘግብረ፡ ሌሊት፡; Image of the Praises of Mary, መልክአ፡ ውዳሴ፡; Image of Mary, መልክአ፡ ማርያም፡; Image of Jesus, መልክአ፡ ኢየሱስ፡; Image of the Archangel Michael, መልክአ፡ ሚካኤል፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="82r" facs="005">Fols 1r–82r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3575Mashaf">Maṣḥafa
                                                  saʿātāt</title>
                     <note>For the Night Hours</note>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>፡፡ ሰዓታት፡ ዘግብረ፡ ሌሊት፡ ሃሌ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ አአትብ[፡] ወእትነሣእ፡ በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሠለስተ፡ አስማተ፡ ነሢእየ፡ እትመረጐዝ፡ እመኒ፡ ወደቁ፡ እትነሣእ፡ ወእመኒ፡ ሖርኩ፡ ውስተ፡ ጽልመት፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ያበርህ፡ ሊተ፡ በእግዚአብሔር፡ ተወከልኩ፡፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                 <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="82r" to="95v" facs="086">Fols 82r–95v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1869Malkea">Malkǝʾa wǝddāse
                                                  Māryām</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ፈቀደ፡ እግዚእ፡ ለአዳም፡ ያግዞ፡ ሥጋኪ፡ ንጹሐ፡ አመ፡ ረሰየ፡ አራዞ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="96r" to="109v" facs="100">Fols 96r–109v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2891RepCh172">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Māryām</title>

                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ሰላም (added above)፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምኪ፡ ሐዋዝ፡፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from="109v" to="121v" facs="114">Fols 109v–121v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2839RepCh123">Malkǝʾa
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                    ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ስመ፡ መሐላ፡ ዘኢሄሱ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                  </incipit>
                </msItem>
